# 🐧 Penguin Clustering Project

This project applies unsupervised machine learning to cluster penguin species using the Palmer Penguins dataset.

## 📊 Features Used
- Bill length (mm)
- Bill depth (mm)
- Flipper length (mm)
- Body mass (g)

## 🧠 Techniques
- StandardScaler for feature scaling
- K-Means clustering (k=3)
- PCA for 2D visualization
- Silhouette Score: **0.498**

## 🛠 Tools
- Python, pandas, seaborn, scikit-learn, matplotlib

